# Usage

<!--startCode-->
```bash
zaruba env write --help
```
 
<details>
<summary>Output</summary>
 
```````
Write envMap to file

Usage:
  zaruba env write <fileName> <envMap> [prefix] [flags]

Flags:
  -h, --help   help for write
```````
</details>
